snippet.title: New Dragon Kingdom Official Trailer
snippet.description:
New updated trailer for Dragon Kingdom. Shows all the current features that the game has available to players!

Thanks for watching! Please check out my facebook, patreon and kickstarter! I would greatly appreciate any support!
